{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_05_01_short",
  "title": "fran 1話 ああ、お金がほしいわ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お金がほしいわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I want money…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか、いきなり……\nでも、ないですね。いつもお金の話ばかりしてますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh‚ what's wrong‚ all of a sudden…\nWell‚ actually not a sudden. You always talk about money.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "失礼ですね、人を金の亡者みたいに\n年末は何かと出費がかさむので、ただの愚痴です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How rude‚ you are treating me like money-mad.\nIt's just a complaint‚ because expenses pile up at the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5666669846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ新曲出ますし、クリスマスにはライブもありますし\n仕事があれば、ギャラも入るからいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we have a new song coming out‚ and a live concert on Christmas.\nIf there's work‚ the pay will come in‚ so it’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2000003179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ年末は、テレビの収録スケジュールやら何やら\n前倒しになって、きついったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at the end of the year‚ things like TV recording schedules and whatnot\nget moved up‚ so it’s tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.83333505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "厳しい日程でお願いしてしまって、すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for asking you to work on such a tight schedule…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5000017167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "まー、kanaは仕事ぎちぎちの中でも\n楽しそうにクリスマス配信の仕込みをしてますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ even in this hectic‚ kana seems to be enjoying\npreparing for the Christmas live stream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.03333505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "私も正直、浮かれたカップル眺めてたって\n鬱陶しいだけですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I just find it annoying\nto look at lovey-dovey couples.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9666683834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "mihoだけはこの時期になると\nいつにも増して辛気くさいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this time‚ only miho gets\neven more gloomy than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2666711808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、忙しいうちが華とはいえ\nちょっとくらい、年末らしいこともしたいですねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ even though it is said that busy times are the best‚\nI’d like to do something to feel the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}